Colombian drain. Right?

21:24.922 --> 21:29.000
'cause there's, you know,
no suicide watch here.

21:29.200 --> 21:30.500
You know what I mean?

21:32.300 --> 21:33.958
Vince, we can't afford Gaghan.

21:34.200 --> 21:35.931
We've got to get a list
of cheaper writers.

21:36.021 --> 21:37.304
He'll have to go for it.

21:37.400 --> 21:38.700
Don't use the word cheap.

21:38.829 --> 21:42.454
I'm heading to makeup,
see you on set. Hey, be firm.

21:42.543 --> 21:44.400
Have I not been?
Have I not been firm?

21:45.838 --> 21:46.897
What's going on?

21:47.000 --> 21:49.594
He's interrogating the crew to find out
who's been with his girl.

21:49.696 --> 21:51.300
- Fuck you.
- No, fuck you.

21:52.000 --> 21:54.800
I'm going to ask you
one time, chochito.

21:56.000 --> 21:58.789
