I'm not going to be happy.

21:58.900 --> 22:00.232
You understand what I'm saying?

22:00.300 --> 22:01.900
I do, Billy, I do.

22:02.108 --> 22:04.100
And I'm not lying.
I swear.

22:04.300 --> 22:07.049
I never touched her.
Never.

22:07.300 --> 22:08.347
Next.

22:10.913 --> 22:11.971
What's up, suit?

22:11.997 --> 22:13.731
- We need to talk, now.
