of getting any more.

22:51.179 --> 22:53.300
- I'll get rid of the extra army guys.
- Not enough.

22:53.400 --> 22:55.600
And lose the Bogata
central library massacre.

22:55.700 --> 22:57.448
- You love that scene.
- I'm compromising.

22:57.600 --> 23:00.200
